      "rationale": "Linear elastic isotropic material model for Ti-6Al-4V is well-supported for sub-yield loading. Rigid UHMWPE fixation block assumption was validated by separate coupon tests showing negligible block deformation. Sensitivity analysis confirmed that interface friction coefficient variation from 0 to 0.3 changed stiffness QoI by less than 2%."
