      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties, geometry, and loading parameters sourced from measurements with documented uncertainty; sensitivity analysis performed.",
      "rationale": "Titanium elastic modulus sourced from lot-specific tensile coupon tests (E = 114 ± 3 GPa). Screw and rod geometry from CMM measurements of production hardware. Applied displacement ramp matches ASTM F1717 protocol. Probabilistic sensitivity analysis (Monte Carlo, N=1000) quantified combined input uncertainty contribution to stiffness QoI as ±2.8%."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
