      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws, production rods, and UHMWPE fixation blocks per ASTM F1717. Hardware sourced from the same production lot as clinical devices. Sample size provides 80% power to detect 10% QoI difference at alpha=0.05."
    },
    {
