      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios including at least two load magnitudes or configurations.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard compression-bending configuration at room temperature. Only one load condition was evaluated; multi-condition testing was not performed due to resource constraints. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the direct correspondence between the single test condition and the primary COU loading scenario."
    },
