      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9: stiffness 1.41, yield force 1.41, force at 40 mm 1.18. All values below 1.96 threshold. Maximum percent difference across all QoIs and ensemble members is 7.3%. Both acceptance criteria satisfied."
    },
    {
