    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. One factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) falls below the required level due to single-condition testing; this gap is accepted because the single test condition directly corresponds to the primary COU loading scenario and all quantitative acceptance criteria are satisfied. Validation metric E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% confirmed for all three QoIs across the full FEA ensemble. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be applied prior to regulatory submission.",
